 SG_ LockStatus : 10|2@1+ (1,0) [0|3] "" InstrumentCluster,GatewayECU

BO_ 1040 LightingControl: 3 BodyControl
 SG_ HeadlightsOn    : 0|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] "" GatewayECU
 SG_ HighBeamOn      : 1|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] "" GatewayECU
