 SG_ TurnSignalRight : 5|1@1+ (1,0) [0|1] "" GatewayECU

BO_ 2016 DiagResponseEngine: 8 EngineECU
 SG_ ResponseService : 0|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "" OBDII
 SG_ ResponsePID     : 8|8@1+ (1,0) [0|255] "" OBDII
 SG_ ResponseData    : 16|48@1+ (1,0) [0|0] "" OBDII